<span style="font-size:small;">or <i>Drachenkampf</i></span></th></tr><tr><td style="padding:0.2em 0 0.4em;padding:0.2em"><a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/File:Destruction_of_Leviathan.png" class="image" title="The Destruction of Leviathan by Gustave Doré (1865)"><img alt="The Destruction of Leviathan by Gustave Doré (1865)" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/9/9d/Destruction_of_Leviathan.png/200px-Destruction_of_Leviathan.png" decoding="async" width="200" height="249" srcset="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/9/9d/Destruction_of_Leviathan.png/300px-Destruction_of_Leviathan.png 1.5x, http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/9/9d/Destruction_of_Leviathan.png/400px-Destruction_of_Leviathan.png 2x" data-file-width="504" data-file-height="627" /></a></td></tr><tr><td style="padding:0.3em 0.4em 0.3em;font-weight:bold;border-top: 1px solid #aaa; border-bottom: 1px solid #aaa;font-style:italic;">
